00:13.522 --> 00:15.105
Wait, you think
this is a snowstorm?

00:15.107 --> 00:17.724
This is nothing.
I'll tell you about a snowstorm.

00:17.726 --> 00:20.694
It was winter break,
freshman year of college...

00:20.696 --> 00:22.295
<i>Marshall and I were</i>
<i>roommates, but we weren't</i>

00:22.297 --> 00:23.897
<i>- really good friends yet.</i>
<i>- Wait, stop.</i>

00:23.899 --> 00:25.365
You've told me this one before.

00:25.367 --> 00:26.483
