00:35.644 --> 00:37.127
<i>You took a back road,</i>
<i>ran out of gas,</i>

00:37.129 --> 00:39.612
<i>got stuck in a snowstorm,</i>
<i>spooned to stay warm--</i>

00:39.614 --> 00:40.997
<i>at least that's your story--</i>

00:40.999 --> 00:43.166
<i>and at the end of it,</i>
<i>you were best friends.</i>

00:43.168 --> 00:46.469
Okay. Okay, that's fine,
because guess what.

00:46.471 --> 00:47.888
That wasn't even the worst
snowstorm ever.

00:47.890 --> 00:49.456
It was 2008...

00:49.458 --> 00:50.891
<i>- Barney and I...</i>
<i>- Took over the bar,</i>

00:50.893 --> 00:53.059
<i>met the Arizona Tech</i>
<i>marching band-- "Go Hens!"--</i>

00:53.061 --> 00:54.394
<i>and they played</i>
<i>"Auld Lang Syne" when Marshall</i>

00:54.396 --> 00:56.229
<i>picked up Lily at the airport.</i>

00:56.231 --> 00:59.099
Okay. Have I told you about
the time that Marshall...

00:59.101 --> 01:01.518
<i>Tried to put Christmas lights</i>
<i>on Lily's grandparents' house</i>

01:01.520 --> 01:03.303
<i>and the little ragamuffin from</i>
<i>next door left him stranded</i>

01:03.305 --> 01:04.671
<i>on the roof?</i>

01:04.673 --> 01:06.006
Did Lily tell you that one?

01:06.008 --> 01:07.407
Yeah.

01:07.409 --> 01:10.110
Lily used the word "ragamuffin."

01:12.830 --> 01:14.297
So I've told you
all my stories.

01:14.299 --> 01:16.333
I'm afraid so,

01:16.335 --> 01:19.169
I have plenty of stories
that you don't know yet.

01:19.171 --> 01:21.454
Like the one where my
college roommates and I

01:21.456 --> 01:22.655
went to this male strip club...

01:22.657 --> 01:24.507
